{
  "stem": "7683.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- once in a while they give you 25 with the whip over your behind because you didn't look good or you didn't look right or whatever.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But not reason at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then hear somebody got killed for no reason-- shot, I think.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was-- I don't know if someone told you about there was once a-- a group what worked outside the camp, and they killed somebody, a German guard or a Ukrainian guard.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they-- two ran away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the rest, they got caught.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They caught them and brought them back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as punishment, we had to see always how they were all shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So-- this one time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Another time happened-- a similar thing happened to that, and that was a not successful-- not uprising or trying something, but it was-- whatever reason.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then they picked-- except the group what they brought back, plus from the regular group what works in camp-- they picked every tenth to go with them to be shot there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I happened to be in the line like that, number nine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Luck.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So-- and then we have to see how they were shot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So those experience was terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The food was bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The treatment was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Only you are tried always-- I always tried not to be obvious, not to see me, if I could, not to fall apart with anything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That whatever they did, just do the minimum and try not-- not to be caught with them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So that maybe helped me a little bit easier, that I didn't have much to do directly with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gee, how many tapes will it be?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
